1
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:41,060
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:43,990
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:47,870
Mr. Ji,

4
00:01:47,870 --> 00:01:48,759
Ms. Xu is here.

5
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:49,920
Let her in.

6
00:01:56,950 --> 00:01:58,479
Do you know why I called you here?

7
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,120
Yes.

8
00:02:00,740 --> 00:02:02,940
Because the morning shoot was delayed.

9
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:04,430
Delayed?

10
00:02:06,690 --> 00:02:08,490
I specifically reminded you
the day before,

11
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:10,430
and repeatedly stressed that
the crew

12
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:11,150
would arrive at 8:00.

13
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,470
What time did you arrive?

14
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,310
Xu Miyu,

15
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,600
as a forewoman,

16
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:16,590
can you not even fulfill
such a simple request

17
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,430
from a guest?

18
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,630
I arrived at 7:30

19
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:20,870
and kept reminding them.

20
00:02:20,870 --> 00:02:22,180
What's the use of just reminding them?

21
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:23,460
David already said it—

22
00:02:23,490 --> 00:02:24,400
there was so much luggage

23
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,960
piled up in the presidential suite,

24
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:28,340
and the butlers were going in and out,
yet no one cleaned it up.

25
00:02:28,340 --> 00:02:29,329
Ultimately,

26
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,930
the delay was caused
by your irresponsible service.

27
00:02:31,930 --> 00:02:33,770
The guest had 14 suitcases in total.

28
00:02:33,770 --> 00:02:34,750
Every suitcase

29
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:36,610
was filled with her private clothes
and personal items.

30
00:02:36,610 --> 00:02:38,390
Without the guest's permission,

31
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:40,000
we cannot touch any of that luggage.

32
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,960
Couldn't you have just asked David?

33
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,160
I couldn't reach him all day yesterday.

34
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,640
Mr. Ji,

35
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:47,750
with this attitude of hers,

36
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,470
I really can't work with her.

37
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,160
Besides,

38
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,780
Qiao Feifei has been contacting me.

39
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,190
I should have first
arranged a VIP parking space

40
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,840
and the massage package for her.

41
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,070
If it really doesn't work out, I...

42
00:02:57,070 --> 00:02:58,130
Come to me anytime.

43
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,630
Do you feel wronged?

44
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:20,890
No.

45
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,990
But I did look for David.

46
00:03:24,010 --> 00:03:24,760
I couldn't find him.

47
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,760
We are not discussing

48
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:28,130
whether a room butler

49
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,880
should tell a guest in advance

50
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:32,110
to prepare their clothes for the next day,

51
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:34,470
nor are we judging
whether you actually did enough

52
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,870
from yesterday until now.

53
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,550
Because

54
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:38,470
it has already happened.

55
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,610
When facing a problem,

56
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,710
don't waste your time

57
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,520
dwelling on emotions.

58
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:45,780
Instead, you should quickly

59
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:47,970
find a solution.

60
00:03:48,990 --> 00:03:50,440
Truly good service

61
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:52,560
isn't just acting polite.

62
00:03:52,690 --> 00:03:56,350
It's about having the real ability
to solve problems decisively.

63
00:04:02,930 --> 00:04:03,770
I understand.

64
00:04:11,770 --> 00:04:12,400
Recently,

65
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,400
the famous actress Li Bingyan,
who had retired for years,

66
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,580
has gone public with her relationship.

67
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:16,950
At the Purong Hotel in Shanghai,

68
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:18,560
she showed affection
with her younger boyfriend,

69
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,160
causing heated discussions among netizens.

70
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,430
Originally participating alone

71
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,070
in the show "Begin Again",

72
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:23,040
she

73
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,070
now has to be accompanied by an assistant

74
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,270
and escorted by security.

75
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,720
Her net worth skyrocketed overnight.

76
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,450
It is said that

77
00:04:28,450 --> 00:04:29,800
the show's production team
has already designated her

78
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,200
as a regular guest
for the next two seasons.

79
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,570
Zhenzhen,

80
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,270
when you begged me

81
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:38,480
to bring our Feifei

82
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,940
to stay at your Purong,

83
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,260
I believed in your sincerity.

84
00:04:42,510 --> 00:04:43,770
But what is the result?

85
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,430
I put in so much effort

86
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,050
to arrange media exposure for our Feifei.

87
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:51,270
In one instant, it was all stolen
by that person surnamed Li.

88
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:53,770
Just like that,
their side gained countless new followers.

89
00:04:53,770 --> 00:04:55,120
Our Feifei's star power,

90
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,820
the kind that can stir up huge traffic,

91
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:59,200
is not meant to be someone else's
stepping stone.

92
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,000
Tell me, as a top sales rep,

93
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,360
how do you do your job?

94
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,360
I'm sorry.

95
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,800
It's already good enough
that I didn't go looking for you.

96
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,120
How dare you come over here

97
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:09,010
and talk to me about a fan meet-and-greet?

98
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:10,050
Do you think

99
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,830
there's any chance
of us cooperating again?

100
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:13,690
Wei, I'm really sorry.

101
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,820
Really sorry.

102
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:16,310
I'm sorry.

103
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,800
I need to take a call.

104
00:05:24,990 --> 00:05:25,840
Got it.

105
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:26,550
I'm coming.

106
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,830
Calm down, Wei.

107
00:05:33,900 --> 00:05:34,830
I'll find another chance

108
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,870
to win one back for Feifei.

109
00:05:36,890 --> 00:05:38,330
Don't you trust me?

110
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:51,940
Ms. Lu.

111
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,200
Mr. Ji wants to see me.

112
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:57,880
[General Manager's Office]

113
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,270
Come in.

114
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,390
Sorry, I'm late.

115
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,200
Come here.

116
00:06:10,870 --> 00:06:12,070
Let me introduce you.

117
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:12,950
This is

118
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,800
Ms. Brown,

119
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,850
the Commercial Director

120
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:15,720
of Liberty Group.

121
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,720
You're the woman

122
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,120
who inspired Marcos, aren't you?

123
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,270
You're amazing.

124
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,360
You know that he wouldn't stop
speaking about you

125
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,800
until I came here.

126
00:06:23,470 --> 00:06:23,980
Please.

127
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,730
Thank you.

128
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,370
As everything I should have done,

129
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:31,610
I always put my clients' demands first,

130
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:35,120
and we're honored to
reach Marcos' standards.

131
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,360
I promise

132
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,720
we will continue to provide
the best service

133
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:42,040
to you and members of your company.

134
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,270
Thank you.

135
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,270
Oh.

136
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:49,390
Let me extend Marcos' gratitude from him.

137
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,810
If I may?

138
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,640
It's yours.

139
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,600
Thank you.

140
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,800
Dear Ms. Xu,

141
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,600
I feel so lucky

142
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:02,260
to have enjoyed
your incredible butler service

143
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:05,240
at Purong Hotel in Shanghai, China.

144
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,030
My visit to the archives before leaving

145
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:10,830
was the highlight
of my entire trip to China.

146
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:13,120
Thanks for your insight and warmth,

147
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,560
making me feel your genuine service

148
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,120
and care.

149
00:07:16,610 --> 00:07:18,000
I hope my team

150
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,800
can enjoy your
amazing hospitality in the future.

151
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:24,240
Yours sincerely, Marcos Yang.

152
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,120
It is my pleasure.

153
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,680
You deserve it.

154
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:35,040
Thanks to Marcos and you.

155
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,130
Thank you so much.

156
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:55,930
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

157
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:50,720
I'm looking forward for a strong

158
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,980
and long cooperation.

159
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,240
I'm flattered, honestly.

160
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,460
Ms. Xu, it's very nice to meet you.

161
00:07:59,610 --> 00:08:01,160
Hope to see you again.

162
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,920
Definitely. We've just signed the contract

163
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:05,050
so you will definitely see me again.

164
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,800
I'm looking forward
to this great service

165
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,240
next time I come.

166
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,480
Thank you very much.

167
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,480
Thank you.

168
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,560
Secretary Wu,

169
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:13,490
see her out.

170
00:08:13,650 --> 00:08:14,130
Okay.

171
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,360
-Thank you.
-Okay.

172
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:21,350
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

173
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,360
Mr. Ji,

174
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,360
I also put a lot of effort

175
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:28,000
into this order.

176
00:08:28,130 --> 00:08:30,160
I didn't mean to steal Ms. Xu's credit.

177
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,860
Post card.

178
00:08:33,179 --> 00:08:36,390
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

179
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:34,400
Can you handle it well?

180
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,450
I can.

181
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:37,330
I'll trust you one more time.

182
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:39,590
Did you arrange

183
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:41,260
these dishes?

184
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,720
I'm glad you like them.

185
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,450
I don't care what ingredients you use.

186
00:09:45,450 --> 00:09:46,590
If this noodle dish fails,

187
00:09:46,590 --> 00:09:47,640
will you take responsibility?

188
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:48,450
I will.

189
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:52,120
Actually,

190
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,550
your butler is also

191
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:55,170
an excellent chef.

192
00:09:55,270 --> 00:09:57,630
Today's plain noodles were made by her.

193
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,240
I really finished

194
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,600
the plain noodles.

195
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,030
With an attitude like hers,

196
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,720
I really can't work with her.

197
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:07,100
If it really doesn't work out, I...

198
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:08,230
Contact me anytime.

199
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,890
Postcard.

200
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,700
If you want to be like before,

201
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,440
you have to live more
strongly than anyone else.

202
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,740
You have to learn how to climb higher,

203
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:30,410
learn how to fight,
and learn how to take what's yours.

204
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,840
You must make everyone
who looked down on you

205
00:10:30,610 --> 00:10:33,710
[Young Lu Zhenzhen]

206
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,720
regret it!

207
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:34,010
Understand?

208
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:03,310
Regarding the fan meeting,

209
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:05,760
the agency has no intention
of cooperating,

210
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,420
so I'm afraid I have to apologize.

211
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,450
Ms. Lu,

212
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:09,860
can you let us go upstairs

213
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:11,160
to see Feifei just once?

214
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,280
Name your price.

215
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:14,880
Feifei is a very important client of mine.

216
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,960
How could I ruin my career

217
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,380
for a little money?

218
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:19,570
Then, Ms. Lu,

219
00:11:19,590 --> 00:11:21,540
is Li Bingyan also your important client?

220
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:22,530
What do you mean?

221
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,120
We're just worried about Feifei.

222
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:26,540
That Li is not popular,

223
00:11:26,570 --> 00:11:27,750
but she loves to clout-chase.

224
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:29,500
Our Feifei is beautiful and kind,

225
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,790
and can't do anything to her.

226
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,330
But as her fans,

227
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,530
we have an obligation
to get justice for her.

228
00:11:34,530 --> 00:11:35,330
That's right.

229
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,350
We promise not to disturb Sister Feifei,

230
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:38,950
but we must get revenge.

231
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:42,330
You three can't go up
to the presidential suite.

232
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:43,510
You need to swipe a card to go up,

233
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,120
and you also need to register.

234
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,930
Especially since two big stars
are staying up there right now,

235
00:11:47,930 --> 00:11:49,710
the security is very strict.

236
00:11:50,650 --> 00:11:52,330
Ms. Lu, you are very resourceful.

237
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:54,090
We all think you're amazing.

238
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,180
You must have a way.

239
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,720
I really don't have a way.

240
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,630
I'm sorry.

241
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:02,040
You must have a way, Ms. Lu.

242
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:05,600
Otherwise, how could you become

243
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,870
the VIP Account Manager of Purong Hotel?

244
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:08,860
Exactly.

245
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:11,650
You three are quite sweet-talkers,

246
00:12:11,650 --> 00:12:14,710
and your intelligence gathering
is quite impressive.

247
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,480
Seeing that you have such deep sisterhood

248
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,720
with your sister,

249
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,960
I can help you.

250
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,230
But promise me,

251
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,610
not to mention my name to anyone.

252
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:27,290
We promise not to tell.

253
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:39,160
[Duan Aoxiang, 1825]

254
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,840
If we handle him,

255
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:46,040
can we get into the presidential suite?

256
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:50,010
We'll check into the
executive floor
right away.

257
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:50,930
Let's go.

258
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,840
Hello.

259
00:13:10,010 --> 00:13:11,040
Daniel.

260
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:12,390
Where are you going? Going out?

261
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,450
I'm going on a date.

262
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,000
Who are you dating?

263
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,600
Why not invite him to your hotel room?

264
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,720
What are you doing?

265
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:18,860
Did Old Madam send you

266
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:20,020
to spy on me?

267
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:20,920
No.

268
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,400
I'm just afraid you'll miss your medicine.

269
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:25,430
Don't worry.

270
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,200
Ming,

271
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,960
my old friend, is back from Shenzhen.

272
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:29,300
I'm going to see him.

273
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,750
Take it easy.

274
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,240
Behind you!

275
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,830
Bro, do you know how to defend the tower?

276
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,800
Seriously…

277
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,000
Are you stupid?

278
00:14:01,330 --> 00:14:02,120
Mr. Duan.

279
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:03,960
Run!

280
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,240
You can't beat him.

281
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,000
Someone is watching you.

282
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,080
Where?

283
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:10,340
The direction is from your four o'clock.

284
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,380
It looks like the other side disconnected.

285
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,310
Does it?

286
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,960
Did you get a clear look?

287
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,600
Is he really Duan Aoxiang?

288
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:30,080
Yes.

289
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,300
Am I this popular now?

290
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:35,240
Duan...

291
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:36,000
Duan...

292
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:36,720
Duan...

293
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,240
Duan Aoxiang!

294
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,220
Who are you?

295
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:40,590
Who sent you to tail me?

296
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:44,210
We...

297
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,160
We weren't sent to tail you.

298
00:14:46,190 --> 00:14:47,990
We are Qiao Feifei's fans.

299
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,750
We want to go upstairs to find Li Bingyan

300
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:50,840
to avenge Feifei.

301
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:52,600
We need your help.

302
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:56,250
Qiao Feifei's fans

303
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,820
came to find Li Bingyan?

304
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,120
Interesting.

305
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,290
Ms. Xu.

306
00:15:04,430 --> 00:15:06,360
Mr. Tan, are you here to see Daniel?

307
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:08,310
I also dropped by to see you.

308
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:11,320
I just went to my dad's room
to look for him.

309
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,200
He doesn't seem to be here.

310
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,600
Do you know where he went?

311
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:16,130
Mr. Tan seems to have gone out.

312
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:16,760
Did you

313
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,000
call him?

314
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,200
He went out?

315
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,120
I called him,

316
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,450
but he isn't answering.

317
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:26,370
Could something have happened to him?

318
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:30,720
Daniel!

319
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:32,840
Dad!

320
00:15:33,890 --> 00:15:34,610
Daniel!

321
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,470
Dad!

322
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:38,290
It seems he hasn't returned yet.

323
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:39,960
Where did he go?

324
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,630
He hasn't answered his phone all day.

325
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,150
Mr. Tan, don't worry.

326
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:44,620
I remember

327
00:15:44,650 --> 00:15:46,190
Daniel said when he left this afternoon

328
00:15:46,190 --> 00:15:48,200
that he was going to
see a friend named Ming.

329
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,510
Do you have Ming's phone number

330
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:50,720
or his address?

331
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,360
Ming?

332
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,750
I don't.

333
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,450
Wait, I think I've heard this name before.

334
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:58,470
How about this?

335
00:15:58,470 --> 00:16:00,070
I'll give Aunt Wanjun a call.

336
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:02,510
What?

337
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:04,120
No one is at Ming's house.

338
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,790
Mr. Tan, don't worry.

339
00:16:07,330 --> 00:16:08,870
I know a place

340
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,900
that Mr. Tan mentioned to me before.

341
00:16:10,930 --> 00:16:11,600
Wait a moment.

342
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,120
I'll come find you

343
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,200
and take you there.

344
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,390
You're on duty tonight.

345
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,330
I need to go out for a bit.

346
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:19,740
The presidential suite
has no special arrangements tonight.

347
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:21,000
Don't go up there rashly.

348
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,580
If there are any emergencies,

349
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:23,510
contact me immediately.

350
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:24,000
Okay.

351
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:25,630
By the way,

352
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,630
if Mr. Tan comes back,

353
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,510
call me right away.

354
00:16:28,510 --> 00:16:29,000
Okay.

355
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,040
Hello.

356
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:38,860
Executive floor receptionist.

357
00:16:38,990 --> 00:16:39,770
Please wait a moment.

358
00:16:39,770 --> 00:16:40,900
I'll be right there.

359
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,750
Thank you, Mr. Duan.

360
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,220
Keep a low profile.

361
00:17:14,390 --> 00:17:15,079
Mr. Duan,

362
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:16,160
are we really letting them go up?

363
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,530
What if they cause trouble?

364
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:19,640
Isn't it better if they cause trouble?

365
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:21,720
Ji Feng gave me
this red carpet gift package.

366
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:24,589
I was just worrying about
what to give him in return.

367
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:26,030
Let's go.

368
00:17:26,089 --> 00:17:27,890
Let's go home and enjoy the show.

369
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,220
Feifei is right here.

370
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:31,240
Yes.

371
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:42,000
We must find Li Bingyan today!

372
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,000
Who are you?

373
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,350
How did you get up here?

374
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:45,280
It's Li Bingyan.

375
00:18:03,670 --> 00:18:04,670
Mr. Tan!

376
00:18:05,490 --> 00:18:06,140
Here.

377
00:18:07,310 --> 00:18:08,080
Sir,

378
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,110
wake up.

379
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,170
Sir.

380
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:11,080
Dad.

381
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,240
Dad.

382
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:13,530
Dad, wake up.

383
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,830
Is Mr. Tan alright?

384
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:16,550
Sir,

385
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:18,240
Get up and come home with me.

386
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:23,090
[Luo Qingping]

387
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,240
Wake up.

388
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,210
Get up.

389
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,680
Can you get up?

390
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:22,240
Get up.

391
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,240
We're going home.

392
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:33,930
He is sleeping soundly.

393
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:38,310
Thanks a lot for today.

394
00:18:39,120 --> 00:18:41,190
How did you know they'd go there?

395
00:18:41,970 --> 00:18:43,970
Mr. Tan mentioned to me before

396
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,480
that there was a jazz bar

397
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:46,460
he really liked.

398
00:18:46,620 --> 00:18:47,360
Right.

399
00:18:47,390 --> 00:18:48,880
The jazz band's first performance

400
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,920
was also there.

401
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,070
So I figured

402
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:52,270
it must be that place.

403
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,680
You haven't known my father for long,

404
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,010
yet you know him so well.

405
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:58,140
Unlike me,

406
00:18:58,210 --> 00:18:59,900
I've lived with him for so many years,

407
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:02,030
but I act like an idiot.

408
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:04,190
I don't know his past,

409
00:19:04,210 --> 00:19:05,600
nor his preferences.

410
00:19:05,810 --> 00:19:07,090
It's quite shameful.

411
00:19:08,050 --> 00:19:09,070
Don't say that.

412
00:19:09,290 --> 00:19:10,690
You are so busy with work.

413
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,710
[Lu Zhenzhen]

414
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:16,490
Hello?

415
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:23,660
[Luo Qingping] [Lu Zhenzhen]

416
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:23,880
What's wrong?

417
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:24,730
Are you okay?

418
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,490
I have so many missed calls.

419
00:19:26,530 --> 00:19:28,000
My phone was on silent.

420
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:28,740
Oh no.

421
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:31,310
Something must have happened at the hotel.

422
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:32,110
Don't worry.

423
00:19:32,150 --> 00:19:32,780
Driver,

424
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:33,550
please hurry.

425
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,400
We're in a rush.

426
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:34,880
Okay.

427
00:19:41,630 --> 00:19:42,960
Why is Li Bingyan hiding?

428
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,090
Is she afraid to take responsibility?

429
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:44,800
Stop shouting!

430
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,470
Calm down!

431
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:46,510
Everyone, calm down.

432
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,940
-Let's talk this through properly;
don't resort to violence.
-Li Bingyan!

433
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:48,640
Quiet!

434
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,200
I'm calling the police.

435
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,160
What are you doing?

436
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,110
Be careful.

437
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:56,350
Keep your voices down.

438
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:56,920
Stop fighting!

439
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:59,320
The general manager is here. Stop arguing!

440
00:20:06,360 --> 00:20:07,120
Mr. Ji,

441
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,720
you're finally here.

442
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,480
I've been trying to call Ms. Xu,

443
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,750
but I can't reach her.

444
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:19,590
Mr. Ji,

445
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:22,450
I'll have someone arrange
for them to go back and rest.

446
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:24,140
After all, they are hotel guests.

447
00:20:24,140 --> 00:20:25,960
I will personally investigate
and question them later.

448
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,350
Is that alright with you?

449
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,110
Okay.

450
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:34,880
Ms. Xu,

451
00:20:35,510 --> 00:20:36,830
with such a major incident happening
in the presidential suite,

452
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:37,670
where did you go?

453
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:39,640
Do you know how many people
couldn't reach you?

454
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,110
I went...

455
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:40,830
Ms. Xu,

456
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:43,070
we have such important guests
staying in the presidential suite,

457
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:43,790
yet you

458
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:45,230
left them behind and ran off.

459
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:47,160
You made everyone clean up your mess.

460
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,510
As the forewoman of the executive floor,

461
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:49,570
are you competent?

462
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:50,350
Mr. Ji,

463
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,350
you really shouldn't have

464
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:52,160
left such an important guest

465
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:52,920
in her care.

466
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,320
It's too irresponsible.

467
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:57,510
Ms. Xu,

468
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:59,090
your explanation?

469
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,550
Mr. Tan in Room 1810

470
00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:01,880
suddenly went missing.

471
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:03,610
I took his family to look for him

472
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:05,110
and temporarily left my post.

473
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:05,880
I apologize.

474
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:06,920
Where is he?

475
00:21:06,990 --> 00:21:08,200
He has returned to his room to rest.

476
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,440
Did you arrange a caregiver?

477
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,700
His family is with him.

478
00:21:11,020 --> 00:21:11,880
It's a matter of life and death,

479
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,200
so it's indeed urgent.

480
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,160
Alright, Ms. Lu,

481
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,910
go and comfort the guests first.

482
00:21:16,910 --> 00:21:17,520
Yes,

483
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:18,540
I'll go right now.

484
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:22,090
Ms. Xu,

485
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:28,800
I said it's excusable,

486
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:31,720
but don't really think
you're not at fault.

487
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,980
You are the forewoman.

488
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:33,640
Ensuring

489
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,110
the normal operation
of the executive floor

490
00:21:35,110 --> 00:21:36,190
is your duty.

491
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:37,420
If you fail to do this,

492
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:38,960
you are derelict in your duty.

493
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,960
In the future, when you encounter

494
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:41,000
a similar situation,

495
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,860
prepare for both eventualities.

496
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,240
I got it.

497
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:46,640
I didn't think it through this time.

498
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:47,980
I'm sorry.

499
00:21:48,810 --> 00:21:50,000
Go deal with it now.

500
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,550
Hurry up.

501
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,200
[Photos and videos]

502
00:22:00,260 --> 00:22:00,440
[Loading]

503
00:22:01,570 --> 00:22:01,750
[Handling]

504
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:02,180
[Photos and videos]

505
00:22:02,300 --> 00:22:03,880
[It's easier to be recommended
with description.]

506
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,130
[Li Bingyan's security pushing people]

507
00:22:09,770 --> 00:22:11,750
[Li Bingyan's security pushing people,
Qiao Feifei fans being humiliated]

508
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,230
Stop recording!

509
00:22:16,230 --> 00:22:17,500
Why did you push me?

510
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:21,940
Li Bingyan is going to
be dropped by the show.

511
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,680
This is the internal notice document.

512
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:25,410
It will be announced this week.

513
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,790
Two of Li Bingyan's brand endorsements

514
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:31,070
are reportedly going to
be replaced as well.

515
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:33,470
Her agency is going to
sue our Purong Hotel.

516
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,350
Ms. Xu,

517
00:22:34,650 --> 00:22:35,710
what should we do?

518
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:37,180
Sue our hotel?

519
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,790
Is it that serious?

520
00:22:44,790 --> 00:22:45,510
Back then,

521
00:22:45,510 --> 00:22:46,790
when I invited Qiao Feifei to stay

522
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:48,400
at our Purong Hotel,

523
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,510
I waited outside her manager's door,
without food or drink,

524
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:51,590
for two whole nights.

525
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:52,650
What did I do it for?

526
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:54,750
Don't I just want to bring glory

527
00:22:54,750 --> 00:22:56,200
to our Purong Hotel?

528
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:59,350
It's the critical stage
for sales performance,

529
00:22:59,350 --> 00:23:02,200
yet such a bad incident happened
in the presidential suite.

530
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:02,960
Ms. Xu,

531
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:04,000
do you have no sense of responsibility

532
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:05,680
towards our hotel at all?

533
00:23:11,790 --> 00:23:13,880
I will solve my own problems.

534
00:23:14,510 --> 00:23:16,350
You don't need to
put on a show for others here.

535
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,480
Put on a show?

536
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:19,200
What do you mean?

537
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,270
Ms. Lu,

538
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,510
go about your business first.

539
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:23,510
Ms. Xu and I

540
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:26,450
will discuss the follow-up
work arrangements.

541
00:23:27,350 --> 00:23:28,200
Okay, Mr. Ji.

542
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,210
If you need me later,

543
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:31,720
I will go all out.

544
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:42,070
I am sorry, Mr. Ji.

545
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:43,830
I didn't expect this

546
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:46,090
would have such a big impact on the hotel.

547
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:47,550
I will try my best

548
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:49,000
to solve it.

549
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:51,030
I will go find Li Bingyan right now.

550
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:51,850
I'll wait for your results.

551
00:23:51,850 --> 00:23:52,570
Okay.

552
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:07,440
Hello.

553
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:08,240
Excuse me,

554
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,830
is Ms. Li Bingyan here?

555
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,740
She is not here.

556
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:11,880
You are?

557
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:13,030
I'm her lawyer.

558
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:14,510
You can tell me anything.

559
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:15,920
Well,

560
00:24:15,950 --> 00:24:16,920
I would like

561
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:17,790
to ask

562
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:19,740
if you could withdraw
the lawsuit against our hotel.

563
00:24:19,740 --> 00:24:21,030
We can discuss

564
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:21,440
and face any issues together.

565
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,350
Say no more.

566
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:25,000
Ms. Li Bingyan is currently caught
in a public opinion storm.

567
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,110
She is suffering heavy losses.

568
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:28,330
She has entrusted me and my legal team

569
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,290
with full authority
to protect her rights and interests.

570
00:24:30,290 --> 00:24:32,620
Your Purong Hotel's poor management

571
00:24:32,650 --> 00:24:34,800
has damaged my client's reputation

572
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:35,680
and stalled her career.

573
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,510
We are still in the stage of
collecting evidence.

574
00:24:37,510 --> 00:24:39,850
We will contact your hotel's
legal department later.

575
00:24:39,850 --> 00:24:41,240
If you have any questions,

576
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:43,170
we can communicate at the hearing.

577
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:43,940
Sir!

578
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:00,280
[You're my love.]

579
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,160
What's the matter,

580
00:25:03,190 --> 00:25:04,120
Butler Xu?

581
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:05,350
Hello, David.

582
00:25:05,380 --> 00:25:06,700
It's like this.

583
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,680
What happened yesterday

584
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:10,070
has gotten out of control on the internet.

585
00:25:10,100 --> 00:25:11,750
I know you have your considerations,

586
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:13,270
but it has affected our hotel's

587
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:14,510
normal operation.

588
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:16,200
The other party wants to sue us.

589
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,240
So,

590
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:18,000
I want to ask,

591
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,000
can you

592
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:21,590
ask Feifei to tell her fans

593
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:24,000
to calm down a little bit?

594
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:25,150
Calm down?

595
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,380
I'm so angry.

596
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,790
Bullying my fans is bullying me.

597
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,960
I won't give up!

598
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:29,990
Alright, Feifei.

599
00:25:30,010 --> 00:25:30,790
We have a magazine shoot

600
00:25:30,790 --> 00:25:31,960
this afternoon.

601
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:33,400
You won't look pretty if you're angry.

602
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,730
Go change your clothes.

603
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:36,300
Go on.

604
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:41,610
As for what happened yesterday,

605
00:25:41,610 --> 00:25:42,510
strictly speaking,

606
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:44,030
it has nothing to do with us.

607
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,680
So we really can't help.

608
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:46,790
Sorry.

609
00:26:02,550 --> 00:26:03,440
Ms. Xu.

610
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:04,830
What's wrong?

611
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:07,560
The guest in 1906 left this for you.

612
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,030
Mr. Tan left?

613
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:16,550
Mr. Tan!

614
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:19,430
-The program team has made an appointment.
-Mr. Tan!

615
00:26:19,430 --> 00:26:20,490
Okay, come with me.

616
00:26:22,310 --> 00:26:23,240
Mr. Tan!

617
00:26:23,750 --> 00:26:24,560
Ms. Xu.

618
00:26:24,590 --> 00:26:25,720
I can't accept this.

619
00:26:27,250 --> 00:26:29,580
Do you want to open it
and take a look first?

620
00:26:35,490 --> 00:26:36,960
I got this sample

621
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,110
from a friend.

622
00:26:38,130 --> 00:26:39,200
It's handmade,

623
00:26:39,230 --> 00:26:40,310
and the materials aren't expensive.

624
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:41,070
I just want to give it to you

625
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:43,270
to express my feelings.

626
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,970
No pressure this time, right?

627
00:26:45,450 --> 00:26:46,450
It's so beautiful.

628
00:26:46,450 --> 00:26:47,300
Thank you.

629
00:26:47,330 --> 00:26:48,070
I'll accept it.

630
00:26:48,070 --> 00:26:49,200
I'm glad you like it.

631
00:26:53,260 --> 00:26:55,060
There is something in your hair.

632
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:58,280
I'm sorry.

633
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:10,480
It's okay.

634
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:12,570
I'll get going now.

635
00:27:12,570 --> 00:27:13,500
Have a safe trip.

636
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:15,430
Okay.

637
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:25,110
Mr. Ji.

638
00:27:25,690 --> 00:27:27,050
Are you done with your work?

639
00:27:27,050 --> 00:27:28,510
I went to look for Li Bingyan just now,

640
00:27:28,510 --> 00:27:29,640
but I didn't see her.

641
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,330
You didn't see her?

642
00:27:30,330 --> 00:27:31,130
And that's it?

643
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,570
Where is your mind at?

644
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:38,630
Do you only have that one guest
in your eyes?

645
00:27:39,700 --> 00:27:41,330
I just went to see Mr. Tan off.

646
00:27:41,390 --> 00:27:42,160
There's a huge issue

647
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,260
with the presidential suite.

648
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:44,370
I've always believed in you

649
00:27:44,370 --> 00:27:46,520
and bought you time to solve it.

650
00:27:46,550 --> 00:27:47,240
And look at you.

651
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,700
Instead of hurrying up
to figure something out,

652
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:50,760
you're receiving gifts from a guest.

653
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:51,960
Do you think

654
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:53,110
fawning over one guest all day

655
00:27:53,110 --> 00:27:54,590
will secure your position?

656
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:56,560
There are plenty of people
waiting to take your spot.

657
00:27:56,560 --> 00:27:58,140
Tell me if you want to quit.

658
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:34,750
Why did you...

659
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:35,590
Ms. Li!

660
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:36,790
Ms. Li!

661
00:28:38,270 --> 00:28:39,240
Ms. Li,

662
00:28:40,510 --> 00:28:42,350
I am here on behalf of Purong Hotel.

663
00:28:42,350 --> 00:28:45,070
I request that you withdraw
the lawsuit against our hotel.

664
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:47,030
Let's face the media together.

665
00:28:47,030 --> 00:28:47,590
okay?

666
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:48,510
We?

667
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:52,030
Is there a common ground

668
00:28:52,030 --> 00:28:53,440
between you and me?

669
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,630
We are your service provider.

670
00:28:56,650 --> 00:28:57,510
We have always

671
00:28:57,510 --> 00:29:00,120
handled problems from your perspective.

672
00:29:00,150 --> 00:29:02,000
What's more, during this period,

673
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:04,190
haven't we been getting along well?

674
00:29:04,850 --> 00:29:06,270
Playing the emotional card?

675
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,930
Please take a good look at the target.

676
00:29:07,930 --> 00:29:09,960
There is only an employment relationship
between us,

677
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,440
not a friendship.

678
00:29:11,710 --> 00:29:14,190
Your hotel provided hellish service.

679
00:29:14,210 --> 00:29:16,670
Now that something went wrong,
you still want me to be lenient?

680
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:18,060
What a joke.

681
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:19,440
Ms. Li,

682
00:29:20,270 --> 00:29:21,790
right after the incident,

683
00:29:21,790 --> 00:29:23,070
the hotel sent security personnel

684
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:24,350
to handle the situation.

685
00:29:24,350 --> 00:29:25,310
Besides,

686
00:29:25,310 --> 00:29:27,480
it wasn't the hotel
you actually clashed with,

687
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:31,070
but the fans who trespassed onto
the presidential suite floor.

688
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,200
Logically speaking,

689
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,100
you shouldn't be suing the hotel.

690
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:35,430
Of course, I understand

691
00:29:35,430 --> 00:29:38,170
that the agency wants to
use the hotel as a megaphone

692
00:29:38,170 --> 00:29:39,930
to amplify this matter.

693
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:42,430
What do you mean?

694
00:29:42,450 --> 00:29:44,370
Are you making excuses to shift the blame?

695
00:29:44,370 --> 00:29:45,920
Your hotel's management loopholes

696
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,450
caused such a huge conflict

697
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:49,320
and damaged my reputation.

698
00:29:49,340 --> 00:29:51,860
Now you want to wash your hands of it

699
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,960
and avoid taking responsibility?

700
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,610
And another thing.

701
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:01,250
You're just a floor forewoman.

702
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:03,880
How can you talk to me
about an equal position?

703
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,240
Who do you think you are?

704
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,720
Getting along well?

705
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,720
Do you deserve it?

706
00:30:08,070 --> 00:30:09,730
Go back and tell your general manager

707
00:30:09,730 --> 00:30:11,590
to get the best lawyer right away.

708
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:12,720
Let's

709
00:30:13,350 --> 00:30:14,510
see in court.

710
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:16,740
Wait a minute!

711
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,960
Ms. Li.

712
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:23,200
Do I need to remind you?

713
00:30:23,270 --> 00:30:24,200
A couple of days ago,

714
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:26,680
when they were filming
at the VIP entrance,

715
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,240
you intentionally brought your boyfriend

716
00:30:28,240 --> 00:30:29,770
and showed up there, right?

717
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,510
I reminded you the day before

718
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:32,590
that during that time,

719
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:34,750
the program crew
will be filming at the VIP entrance,

720
00:30:34,750 --> 00:30:35,980
and there will be media.

721
00:30:35,980 --> 00:30:38,640
But you just had to
show up at that specific time.

722
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:41,110
Didn't you just use me, a lowly forewoman,

723
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,270
to get the information,

724
00:30:42,270 --> 00:30:43,550
then direct and act in

725
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:45,590
an attention-grabbing drama,

726
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:48,070
and finally push the responsibility
for poor arrangements

727
00:30:48,070 --> 00:30:49,890
onto our hotel?

728
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:50,910
Isn't that right?

729
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:52,530
What are you trying to say?

730
00:30:52,530 --> 00:30:54,470
That being troubled by Qiao Feifei's fans

731
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:55,790
is my own fault?

732
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,840
That's not what I meant.

733
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,440
I came to see you today

734
00:30:59,470 --> 00:31:01,210
not to discuss who is right or wrong,

735
00:31:01,210 --> 00:31:03,270
but to ask you to rationally consider

736
00:31:03,280 --> 00:31:04,680
your current situation.

737
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:06,960
Right.

738
00:31:07,170 --> 00:31:09,150
Although I am just a lowly forewoman,

739
00:31:09,150 --> 00:31:10,520
on an executive level,

740
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:12,270
I am the spokesperson for the hotel.

741
00:31:12,270 --> 00:31:14,270
Today I'm here on behalf of the hotel

742
00:31:14,270 --> 00:31:16,230
to discuss a way forward with you.

743
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,420
In short,

744
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:19,830
if you withdraw
the lawsuit against the hotel,

745
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:22,070
the rewards you receive
will be substantial.

746
00:31:22,070 --> 00:31:23,750
The hotel won't have to put more energy

747
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:26,130
into dealing with
this unreasonable lawsuit.

748
00:31:26,130 --> 00:31:26,890
Then,

749
00:31:26,910 --> 00:31:28,260
we can definitely,

750
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:30,880
with the attitude
and sincerity of an ally,

751
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:33,830
help defend you in public

752
00:31:33,830 --> 00:31:35,460
and recover your losses.

753
00:31:35,590 --> 00:31:36,400
However,

754
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:39,430
if you fail to appreciate
the hotel's good intentions

755
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:41,040
and choose to bite
the hand that feeds you,

756
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:43,310
then this lawsuit
is bound to be a protracted one.

757
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,900
And both sides will suffer.

758
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:47,680
Setting aside our hotel's losses,

759
00:31:48,030 --> 00:31:49,790
during this time,

760
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:52,890
you may face a damaged reputation,

761
00:31:52,910 --> 00:31:54,540
career stagnation,

762
00:31:54,570 --> 00:31:56,420
and fleeting popularity.

763
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:58,310
How quickly
the entertainment industry changes,

764
00:31:58,310 --> 00:32:00,310
I think you know better than anyone.

765
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,070
So,

766
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:03,270
whether to cooperate with us or not,

767
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:05,130
think clearly before you decide.

768
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,440
You're just a floor forewoman.

769
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:32,990
How can you talk to me
about a common position?

770
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,560
Who do you think you are?

771
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:36,000
Getting along happily?

772
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:37,030
Do you deserve it?

773
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,310
Ms. Xu,

774
00:32:50,590 --> 00:32:51,590
you impress me.

775
00:32:52,590 --> 00:32:54,110
Li Bingyan's legal representative

776
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,090
sent me an email,

777
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,030
saying their internal team

778
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:59,760
needs to reconsider
the litigation resolution.

779
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:02,340
It seems your persuasion worked.

780
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:03,200
Good job.

781
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:05,790
That's good.

782
00:33:09,350 --> 00:33:10,350
Mr. Ji is not here.

783
00:33:10,590 --> 00:33:11,920
Are you looking for him?

784
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:12,960
No.

785
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,510
Regarding the hotel's losses,

786
00:33:15,510 --> 00:33:17,200
Mr. Ji has already gone
to figure out a way.

787
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,310
He will bring the program team's
accommodation orders

788
00:33:19,310 --> 00:33:20,400
to the hotel

789
00:33:20,510 --> 00:33:22,790
to try to eliminate the negative impact.

790
00:33:24,350 --> 00:33:25,440
This matter

791
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,240
is considered over.

792
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:29,310
You don't need to blame yourself too much.

793
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:31,070
After all, you were also drawn into

794
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:32,830
this intrigue.

795
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,440
You handled it very well.

796
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,590
In the HSKP Department,

797
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:38,730
it's inevitable to encounter such things.

798
00:33:38,730 --> 00:33:40,480
Even if you are promoted in the future,

799
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:41,480
some things

800
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:43,600
will still require you
to handle them personally.

801
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:46,030
Consider this a trial.

802
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,880
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

803
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,300
I'll go back to work then.

804
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:51,860
Okay.

805
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:12,670
[HSKP Department of Purong Hotel ,Xu Miyu]

806
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,500
Li Bingyan has yielded.

807
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:08,670
Ms. Xu got it done.

808
00:35:23,770 --> 00:35:24,630
Do you think

809
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:25,760
fawning over one guest all day

810
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:27,290
will secure your position?

811
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:29,160
There are plenty of people
waiting to take your spot.

812
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:30,000
If you want to quit,

813
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:30,880
tell me sooner.

814
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:51,370
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

815
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:54,710
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

816
00:35:56,930 --> 00:35:58,840
♪ People in the city ♪

817
00:35:59,660 --> 00:36:02,600
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

818
00:36:04,530 --> 00:36:06,340
♪ The palms of time ♪

819
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:11,380
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

820
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:14,910
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

821
00:36:15,910 --> 00:36:17,950
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

822
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:23,220
It was indeed my fault to begin with.

823
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:24,700
[Civil Complaint]

824
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:25,110
I had some conflicts with the hotel,

825
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:26,400
which led to some misunderstandings,

826
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,480
and even alerted the company's legal team.

827
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,800
Thinking about it now,

828
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:33,860
I am truly ashamed.

829
00:36:37,410 --> 00:36:38,340
Mr. Ji.

830
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:40,920
Bingyan,

831
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,230
long time no see.

832
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,400
Long time no see.

833
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:48,030
Regarding the extreme behavior
of those fans,

834
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,110
the fan club has already stepped in

835
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:50,190
and severely criticized them.

836
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,030
Thank you.

837
00:36:51,490 --> 00:36:52,140
Here.

838
00:36:58,810 --> 00:36:59,510
Mr. Dai,

839
00:36:59,510 --> 00:37:01,310
thank you for your cooperation.

840
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:03,240
You are a reasonable man, Mr. Ji.

841
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:04,800
Technically speaking,

842
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:07,510
the troublemaking fans
are not part of our company.

843
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:10,370
This time, we are willing to cooperate
in mediation

844
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,030
purely out of respect for Mr. Ji.

845
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:12,630
Thank you.

846
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:15,550
But there is one thing I must make clear.

847
00:37:18,550 --> 00:37:19,510
Please go ahead.

848
00:37:20,130 --> 00:37:21,220
I heard that

849
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,400
these fans went up

850
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,190
with a guest

851
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:25,440
who previously stayed
in the presidential suite.

852
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,510
the presidential suite.

853
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:26,920
Yes.

854
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:28,630
We have checked the surveillance video.

855
00:37:28,630 --> 00:37:29,630
Then,

856
00:37:30,110 --> 00:37:31,640
how do they know each other?

857
00:37:35,240 --> 00:37:36,320
I also heard

858
00:37:36,410 --> 00:37:37,770
that the person who introduced them

859
00:37:37,770 --> 00:37:40,440
was the VIP manager
of your sales department—

860
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:41,400
Lu Zhenzhen.

861
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:44,640
I've dealt with her before.

862
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,910
As long as it benefits her,

863
00:37:46,930 --> 00:37:47,590
she would certainly

864
00:37:47,590 --> 00:37:48,920
do something like this.

865
00:37:52,970 --> 00:37:55,620
[General Manager's Office]

866
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,020
Mr. Ji,

867
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:04,520
do I need to communicate with
Li Bingyan's side?

868
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:09,040
How did Qiao Feifei's fans
get to the presidential suite?

869
00:38:09,080 --> 00:38:10,120
I have no idea.

870
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,480
Didn't they come to you?

871
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:13,590
Weren't you the person
in charge of the fan meeting?

872
00:38:13,590 --> 00:38:14,280
Mr. Ji,

873
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,480
they asked me about Mr. Duan Jr.

874
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:16,880
I was also...

875
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,190
Did they ask about it

876
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:20,000
or did you leak it on purpose?

877
00:38:20,020 --> 00:38:21,750
Of course they asked.

878
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:24,520
Leaking a guest's information privately
is a serious dereliction of duty.

879
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:26,240
Are you clear on how it should be handled

880
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:28,070
according to industry regulations?

881
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:29,510
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

882
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:32,150
I was really pushed too far by them

883
00:38:32,170 --> 00:38:33,630
and acted without thinking.

884
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:34,800
Mr. Ji, you must give me a chance

885
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,280
to make up for it.

886
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:38,260
I happen to have a few major clients

887
00:38:38,290 --> 00:38:39,410
about to close.

888
00:38:39,430 --> 00:38:40,840
I promise that this quarter,

889
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:43,700
I can bring at least
three large orders to the hotel.

890
00:38:46,310 --> 00:38:48,510
Your bonus for one quarter
will be deducted.

891
00:38:48,510 --> 00:38:50,630
You said three large orders yourself.

892
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:52,030
If you can't do it, you'll be fired.

893
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:52,670
Also,

894
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,900
I don't know what your habits were before,

895
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:55,820
but here,

896
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:57,890
stop playing dirty

897
00:38:57,910 --> 00:38:59,230
and taking shortcuts.

898
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,030
Mr. Ji, I know I was wrong.

899
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,550
I will never do it again.

900
00:39:11,510 --> 00:39:12,440
Mr. Zhao,

901
00:39:12,470 --> 00:39:14,910
Purong Hotel is certainly very sincere.

902
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:16,980
[Customer information
Yinhe Zhichuang Exhibition Planning Group]

903
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:16,840
As for the specific terms,

904
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:19,100
how about we set up
a time to meet and talk?

905
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,000
Tomorrow is fine for me, of course.

906
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:21,600
Zhenzhen.

907
00:39:24,950 --> 00:39:25,720
Mr. Zhao,

908
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:29,120
how about I visit your company personally
tomorrow afternoon?

909
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:30,230
Don't you know me?

910
00:39:30,230 --> 00:39:31,700
We've known each other for so long.

911
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,550
I will definitely give you the best plan.

912
00:39:33,550 --> 00:39:34,400
Zhenzhen.

913
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:37,840
Okay.

914
00:39:38,190 --> 00:39:40,050
Okay, Mr. Zhao, see you tomorrow.

915
00:39:44,170 --> 00:39:45,180
[Approval] [Lu Zhenzhen's outing request]

916
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,320
Why did you drink so much?

917
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,120
Didn't you see I was on the phone?

918
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:52,510
I had a social engagement tonight.

919
00:39:52,510 --> 00:39:53,910
I drank a little too much.

920
00:39:54,310 --> 00:39:55,970
Then you should get some rest.

921
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,990
I still have to work overtime for a while.

922
00:39:57,990 --> 00:39:59,550
Can you cook some porridge for me?

923
00:39:59,550 --> 00:40:00,940
My stomach is not feeling well.

924
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:02,370
Can you just order some takeout yourself?

925
00:40:02,370 --> 00:40:05,030
Won't the takeout be cold
by the time it arrives?

926
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:07,440
Nie Yucheng,

927
00:40:09,410 --> 00:40:11,200
I'm not your mother.

928
00:40:11,310 --> 00:40:12,680
Ji Feng keeps an eye on me every day now.

929
00:40:12,680 --> 00:40:14,610
I'm under a lot of pressure at work.

930
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:16,960
If you think I can't serve you well,

931
00:40:16,990 --> 00:40:18,450
I'll get you a nanny, okay?

932
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:21,800
Okay.

933
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,260
You get back to work. Okay.

934
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:28,960
The medicine is in the living room drawer.

935
00:40:38,870 --> 00:40:39,760
Hurry, give me the bowl.

936
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,760
It smells so good.

937
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:44,400
This is the newly arrived
Nanhui salted meat.

938
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:45,800
The quality is excellent.

939
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:47,860
Judging by your look, it's in the bag.

940
00:40:48,250 --> 00:40:49,850
It's almost a done deal.

941
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,970
Have a taste. How is it?

942
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,070
Thank you.

943
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:56,670
Wait.

944
00:40:58,070 --> 00:40:59,400
I suggest

945
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:01,190
you take a sip of soup first

946
00:41:01,220 --> 00:41:02,970
to open up your taste buds,

947
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:04,070
and then eat the food.

948
00:41:04,070 --> 00:41:05,070
So particular.

949
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:06,960
Alright, I'll listen to you.

950
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,670
You should taste it first.

951
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:14,710
Your head is almost
falling into the soup bowl.

952
00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:15,360
No, no, no.

953
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:17,110
You... you taste it first.

954
00:41:24,510 --> 00:41:25,840
How is it?

955
00:41:28,670 --> 00:41:30,000
Is it not good?

956
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:33,080
Let me taste it.

